{"tid":309283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門菜園村居民被狂加租迫遷　遭恐嚇若不搬走「連累家人」","createTime":"2017-07-05T01:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T03:43:21.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c2f2b91e9919e712e3539c6ffccc7b781edcfe0f","tid":309283,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T01:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/kwong-01_OecKO_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fkwong-01_OecKO_1200x0.png&h=c028714c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n門泥圍菜園村上月起由「森林發展建設有限公司」負責租務，即向村內逾一百戶居民加租、逼遷。村內更出現一張恐嚇通告，稱居民若不搬走將會「後果自負，連累家人」。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨鄺俊宇接到泥圍菜園村村民的求助，稱遭到業主逼遷及恐嚇，他今日到村內了解情況。鄺俊宇指該處為屏山祖堂地，居民稱不少人已於該村住數十年，一直都以年租租用土地及向祖堂交租。不過上月一間名為「森林發展建設有限公司」接手租務，並向居民大幅加租，由每年租金為6,000元，大增至7萬元。<br />\n<br />\n近日村內更出現一張無下款的通告，當中列明「泥圍菜園村所有村民於2017年10月23日前全部遷出。如不搬出！後果自負！連累家人！」鄺俊宇批評，業主以恐嚇形式的收地手法是卑鄙及不合理，當中更涉出言恐嚇，完全無視法治。他將去信警方要求介入調查。<br />\n<br />\n翻查公司註冊處的資料，「森林發展建設」是由徐森林擔任唯一股東兼董事，他同時是「香港豐順同鄉聯誼總會」的董事之一。該會在2013年舉行首屆會董就職，獲時任立法會主席曾鈺成、中聯辦九龍工作部部長何靖、港島工作部副部長陳偉、梅州市副市長陳麗霞等人現身支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E8%8F%9C%E5%9C%92%E6%9D%91%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E8%A2%AB%E7%8B%82%E5%8A%A0%E7%A7%9F%E8%BF%AB%E9%81%B7-%E9%81%AD%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87%E8%8B%A5%E4%B8%8D%E6%90%AC%E8%B5%B0-%E9%80%A3%E7%B4%AF%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E8%258F%259C%25E5%259C%2592%25E6%259D%2591%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%258B%2582%25E5%258A%25A0%25E7%25A7%259F%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E9%2581%25B7-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%2581%2590%25E5%259A%2587%25E8%258B%25A5%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2590%25AC%25E8%25B5%25B0-%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%25B4%25AF%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&d=aBFxeDEzZrt8zq9XuNrUMp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=afaea58f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E8%258F%259C%25E5%259C%2592%25E6%259D%2591%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%258B%2582%25E5%258A%25A0%25E7%25A7%259F%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E9%2581%25B7-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%2581%2590%25E5%259A%2587%25E8%258B%25A5%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2590%25AC%25E8%25B5%25B0-%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%25B4%25AF%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&h=e2a64cae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E8%8F%9C%E5%9C%92%E6%9D%91%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E8%A2%AB%E7%8B%82%E5%8A%A0%E7%A7%9F%E8%BF%AB%E9%81%B7-%E9%81%AD%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87%E8%8B%A5%E4%B8%8D%E6%90%AC%E8%B5%B0-%E9%80%A3%E7%B4%AF%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA/</a>"},{"pid":"4444af2dade7dc527b2b8caf1becbe78fca416b5","tid":309283,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T02:31:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db66de810f719ece6672c50c7e736173a21e3e9b","tid":309283,"uid":54832,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T02:41:31.000Z","msg":"屌你 每年6000$住左咁耐<br />\n加租都無可厚非"},{"pid":"e6c9e610ffacb63237ea6f5cae82bd1d572f7f5f","tid":309283,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T02:43:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你 每年6000$住左咁耐<br />\n加租都無可厚非</blockquote><br />\n咪係 果面仲有大量劏房係度 九世係租上租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543bf0d8f0b7b1fce365a4e6447a10a81a1fb0e7","tid":309283,"uid":10894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T02:59:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7eb6a5c8fb2eea0be5beab3551ff8c2bd84e10dc","tid":309283,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:02:50.000Z","msg":"全部人加埋交7萬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6b2a27f2025fc4c9754f0882e0a25330725d55","tid":309283,"uid":48083,"like":1,"