ockquote><br />\n<br />\n租一件事<br />\n上面渉嫌刑事恐嚇喎</blockquote><br />\n恐嚇咪報警<br />\n逼咩遷?<br />\n好似當正塊地係自己既咁<br />\n<br />\n老老柒柒可能係自己恐嚇自己駁上報添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用恐嚇叫人走=迫遷<br />\n<br />\n自己恐嚇自己??<br />\n不如話你係五毛仲有可能啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883469eb9df92a42d5d05b7d57fedbc80d4544c7","tid":309283,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/111525_37747d6871acb2ae1a52e4cddd5831a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F111525_37747d6871acb2ae1a52e4cddd5831a9.jpg&h=40698c0e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/111539_5ad93974ad5c8536d93faf4b774b2b8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F111539_5ad93974ad5c8536d93faf4b774b2b8c.jpg&h=f0bb41e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/111540_cb5119731e29294706888ccefd10e9bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F111540_cb5119731e29294706888ccefd10e9bd.jpg&h=88cf3053&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7a7b4a4b3040e6b9fdc036408e8e4cb456adc66","tid":309283,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:16:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc539ad47add80888c529572a51e4fbf8777a58f","tid":309283,"uid":122718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:18:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c40ebc7fc4982223bd08ad82e95bd83b6df8dd3","tid":309283,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:36:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1bfe8173f0afaf5a772dfa85529f394945d11973","tid":309283,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:39:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拿, 我無斷定村民用苦肉計呀<br />\n我只係指出, 有恐嚇message貼出黎, 唔等於恐嚇者就係地主<br />\n恐嚇者一樣有機會可以係村民自己, 係件案未查清楚時唔應該斷定係邊個做<br />\n再者, 就算證實恐嚇者真係地主, 咁咪拉佢坐監<br />\n7萬年租佢依然有權收<br />\n就算人地係監倉收你都吹佢唔脹架wor</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n機會有大有細<br />\n原則上進化論都有&quot;機會&quot;係錯<br />\n<br />\n兩邊都有機會<br />\n不過建制地主出黑社會大把先例<br />\n租戶自己恐嚇自己有冇一單前科?"},{"pid":"542651a55dffda91b7a1958cce1bb3cf85d37d62","tid":309283,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:40:24.000Z","msg":"報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e273e9d55c6c065481cd6431bb939f704ba47ed","tid":309283,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:43:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}